{"tid":1114144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運輸署建議開放八號幹線沙田段予紅色小巴行走","createTime":"2019-04-18T10:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T10:02:13.000Z","uid":244704,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b9de0eef351c21c49c8e58d07bace37548e7f755","tid":1114144,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"估計因為新界東塞車嚴重，即使運輸署不喜歡紅色小巴，不想太多紅色小巴行獅子山隧道，所以開放禁區。<br />\n<br />\n如果禁區開放成功，相信不少紅色小巴路線使用。<br />\n<br />\n區議會文件<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/ssp/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_doc/TAC/17063/SSP_TAC_2019_43.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fssp%2Fdoc%2F2016_2019%2Ftc%2Fcommittee_meetings_doc%2FTAC%2F17063%2FSSP_TAC_2019_43.pdf&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=df2d320b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/ssp/doc/2016_2019/tc/committee_meetings_doc/TAC/17063/SSP_TAC_2019_43.pdf</a>"}]}